description:
As we enter into a new year, there are 3 essential things that every Christian MUST do. As the new year has come upon us, my heart goes out to you  I want you to be ready for the coming events on this earth. I want your family to be safe and secure in the arms of God. I want you to be prepared for eternity. I truly believe that doing these 3 things will prepare you for what is coming.
